00:10:46.926 --> 00:10:49.026 A:middle
up with a logo that looks
something like this.

00:10:49.026 --> 00:10:51.966 A:middle
Something that we see fairly
often, and we, we need to,

00:10:52.586 --> 00:10:53.856 A:middle
to reach out to publishers
to fix.

00:10:54.376 --> 00:10:56.806 A:middle
Also avoid using
just raw photos.

00:10:56.806 --> 00:10:58.466 A:middle
They're going to end
up being really small

00:10:58.466 --> 00:11:00.436 A:middle
in the various places
that we use them in News,

00:10:58.466 --> 00:11:00.436 A:middle
in the various places
that we use them in News,

