00:17:40.216 --> 00:17:42.086 A:middle
So what can you do
with Apple News format?

00:17:42.086 --> 00:17:42.926 A:middle
Why is it so great?

00:17:43.126 --> 00:17:48.406 A:middle
Well, first, we provide a, a
robust content delivery network.

00:17:48.406 --> 00:17:50.306 A:middle
We have points of
presence around the world

00:17:50.306 --> 00:17:52.926 A:middle
that ensures lightning
fast loading and no delay.

00:17:52.926 --> 00:17:54.806 A:middle
Nothing will ensure people
won't read your article

00:17:54.806 --> 00:17:56.426 A:middle
like an article that
doesn't load.

00:17:58.056 --> 00:17:59.846 A:middle
We also supply rich analytics,

00:18:00.836 --> 00:18:03.786 A:middle
and we also automatically
optimize for each device.

00:18:03.786 --> 00:18:06.906 A:middle
Apple News format is really
focused on author wants

00:18:06.906 --> 00:18:10.296 A:middle
and having it look great on
any device automatically.

00:18:11.206 --> 00:18:14.576 A:middle
We provide simple but
powerful monetization tools.

00:18:15.556 --> 00:18:19.166 A:middle
We have a dedicated Apple News
editorial team that's just

00:18:19.166 --> 00:18:21.116 A:middle
looking for great
content every single day,

00:18:21.116 --> 00:18:23.066 A:middle
and that's a huge
opportunity for you

00:18:23.066 --> 00:18:26.326 A:middle
if you're creating really
engaging cool stuff.

00:18:26.546 --> 00:18:28.016 A:middle
We also have built-in
cross promotion.

00:18:28.016 --> 00:18:31.296 A:middle
So if publish an article
using Apple News format,

00:18:31.716 --> 00:18:35.956 A:middle
it's really easy to have at
the bottom of it, more articles

00:18:35.956 --> 00:18:38.846 A:middle
from your channel and related
articles from other channels.

00:18:39.216 --> 00:18:40.816 A:middle
It's a great way to
drive additional traffic.

00:18:41.996 --> 00:18:44.826 A:middle
Apple News format itself
supports lots of cool features

00:18:45.146 --> 00:18:47.956 A:middle
like animations,
parallax, galleries,

00:18:47.956 --> 00:18:50.796 A:middle
videos, photo mosaics.

00:18:50.796 --> 00:18:52.666 A:middle
It's incredibly powerful
and really easy

00:18:52.666 --> 00:18:54.496 A:middle
to add these elements
to your articles.

00:18:55.226 --> 00:18:58.026 A:middle
We also support dynamic
text sizing.

00:18:58.026 --> 00:19:02.806 A:middle
If you have that set in iOS
for improved legibility,

00:18:58.026 --> 00:19:02.806 A:middle
If you have that set in iOS
for improved legibility,

00:19:03.346 --> 00:19:05.506 A:middle
and then we're also
very accessible.

00:19:05.506 --> 00:19:07.366 A:middle
We have great support for
the accessibility features

00:19:07.366 --> 00:19:08.626 A:middle
in iOS like voice over.

00:19:08.996 --> 00:19:11.146 A:middle
And we have lots of
options for delivery

00:19:11.316 --> 00:19:13.476 A:middle
of content into Apple News.

00:19:13.546 --> 00:19:17.306 A:middle
So lots of advantages to
using Apple News format.

